# 🛸 TRAVERSE: Multi-UAV Path Planner

[![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/)
[![FastAPI](https://img.shields.io/badge/FastAPI-0.95%2B-009688.svg)](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/)
[![TensorFlow](https://img.shields.io/badge/TensorFlow-2.5%2B-FF6F00.svg?style=flat&logo=tensorflow)](https://tensorflow.org/)
[![PyTorch](https://img.shields.io/badge/PyTorch-1.9%2B-EE4C2C.svg?style=flat&logo=pytorch)](https://pytorch.org/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)

**TRAVERSE** is a production-grade, state-of-the-art **Multi-UAV Path Planning** application and programmatic library. It integrates classical heuristics, dynamic replanning, reinforcement learning, and swarm intelligence algorithms into a unified, high-performance package with an interactive, gorgeous real-time web visualization GUI dashboard.

---

## 🌟 Key Features

* **Advanced Algorithm Stack**: Features 6 state-of-the-art pathfinding solvers:
  * **Classical & Dynamic**: **A\* Heuristics** and **D\* Lite (Dynamic A\*)**
  * **Tabular RL**: **Tabular Q-Learning**
  * **Deep RL**: **Deep Q-Networks (DQN)** and **Soft Actor-Critic (SAC)** (TensorFlow/Keras backend)
  * **Swarm Intelligence**: **Hybrid PSO-SAC** (PyTorch backend, imitating Greedy Swarm Planners)
* **Gorgeous Interactive Web GUI**: Real-time canvas visualization of UAV flights, custom obstacle placing tools, start/goal repositioning, and performance metrics graph dashboards.
* **Unified CLI Command (`traverse`)**: Plug-and-play installation exposes a sleek terminal CLI to launch servers or run instant terminal simulations.
* **Optimized Deep RL Engines**: Completely vectorized mini-batch calculations for deep reinforcement learning models, completing 5000 train-test episodes up to **100x faster** than naive loops.
* **Clean Programmatic API**: Reusable Python package imports to integrate pathfinding solvers inside third-party robotic libraries.

---

## 📂 Codebase Reorganization & Packaging

The repository has been structured as a standard installable Python package named `traverse` to ensure perfect encapsulation, reuse, and plug-and-play execution.

```
Multi-UAV-Path-Planner/
├── traverse/                 # Core packaged source directory (previously 'app')
│   ├── __init__.py           # Exposes public library API
│   ├── main.py               # FastAPI backend & uvicorn server runner
│   ├── algorithms.py         # Unified planner entrypoint
│   ├── astar.py              # A* search planner module
│   ├── dstarlite.py          # D* Lite incremental planner module
│   ├── qlearning.py          # Tabular Q-Learning planner module
│   ├── deep_rl.py            # TensorFlow-backed DQN & SAC models
│   ├── pso_sac.py            # PyTorch-backed Hybrid PSO-SAC imitation learning model
│   ├── cli/                  # Command line entrypoint directory
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   └── main.py           # Subcommand parsers (traverse gui / traverse plan)
│   └── templates/
│       └── index.html        # Premium, responsive HTML/JS visualization client
├── A-star.py                 # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for A*
├── D-star.py                 # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for D* Lite
├── q_learning.py             # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for Q-Learning
├── DQN.py                    # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for Deep Q-Network
├── SAC.py                    # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for Soft Actor-Critic
├── Hybrid_PSO_SAC.py         # Fully-functional CLI wrapper for Hybrid PSO-SAC
├── requirements.txt          # Package installation prerequisites
├── pyproject.toml            # Modern pip install packaging configuration
└── setup.py                  # Classic setuptools installation script
```

